%^BOLD%^-=%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Good Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing fully upon the forces of pure good, this domain blesses
those of like hearts while harming most those who are directly
opposite in beliefs.  However, the spells involved will still
affect those even of the same alignment.  Most spells will only
work for a priest of good alignment.

Clerics with the Good Domain gain the following benefits:
- Use of the %^CYAN%^BOLD%^enhance%^RESET%^ command to place the holy enhancement on your weapon.
- +5 damage resistance against evil opponents.

The good domain contains the following spells:

Protection from Alignment, Align Weapon, Prayer, Holy Smite, Burst of Glory, Holy Orb, Holy Word, Holy Aura, Gate

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Callamir, Jarmila, Kreysneothosies

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
